.
 Untis manages multiple schedule specific objects such as curricula, modules
 and subjects among many others.
 These resources have import and export interfaces to multiple systems,
 some of which are responsible for the management of other some of the same
 resources.
 The schedule planning in itself has strong dependencies with the content
 and temporal behavior of other university specific processes.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Building on the gaining predominance of Joomla! 2.5.x and Untis within the
 THM, the interface between these two systems has gained much on importance
 over the course of the last year.
 This interface, THM Organizer, was developed as software for the Joomla!
 CMS which is capable of importing Untis XML export files.
 This import then serves as the basis for a multitude of university specific
 functions.
\end_layout

